<L>Straight vow'd revenge, and &s;eiz'd the pointed dart;</L>
<L>And ere the &s;ound had well expir'd</L>
<L>'Twas whirl'd, and as it fled it fir'd;</L>
<L>The virgin felt it glowing in her heart:</L>
<L>Eugenia &s;igh'd, "Yes! now I know</L>
